29.99 per cent.
Dr Norbert Froemmer and Dr Bernhard Ebner are to join the Telfos board as
Jenbacher's representatives.
As planned, following the completion of the capital injection, Mr Stephen
Cockburn is stepping down as chairman and a director and Mr Douglas Morton
has been invited to act as chairman.
